The Feed the Future Innovation Lab for Legume Systems is seeking cutting-edge legume systems research proposals for Area of Inquiry 1 - Integration of legumes into sustainable smallholder farming systems and agricultural landscapes. The deadline for submission of concept notes is May 20, 2019. For more information on eligibility and requirements visit our website or piestar. The Legume Systems Innovation Lab will focus on three areas of inquiry: Calls for concept notes for AOI2 and AOI3 will be forthcoming. A webinar will be held on April 16, 2019 at 11am Eastern Daylight Time in the U.S. (GMT/UTC -4 hours) to address any questions regarding the request for concept notes for Area of Inquiry 1. Registration is required.